Maintainer: Brendan Ansell <ansell.b@wehi.edu.au>
Description: Provides functions to scale, log-transform and run linear models within tidyr / dplyr chains.
    Intended for smoothing over inconsistencies from base R statistical functions, allowing ease of teaching, learning and daily use.
